Entries.default: "The Vailian Trading Company calls Queen's Berth its home."
"Be sure you make time to visit Serpent's Crown. It is the jewel of our city."
"Further up the mountain, Periki's Overlook is where art and wealth come together."
"We do not see many like you in Neketaka. I will hope your coming is a good sign."
"This district grows more foreign by the day."
"Rauatai plans to settle for good. I have concerns about our safety."
"The green man will not come here, yes?"
"May the fish leap into your boat."
